# All Contributors specification

This repository uses the [All Contributors](https://allcontributors.org/) specification.

## Adding Contributors

Run the following command to add a new contributor:

```bash
npx all-contributors-cli add <username> <contribution-types>
```

Example:
```bash
npx all-contributors-cli add TangBoheng code,doc,ideas
```

### Contribution Types

| Emoji | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| 💻 | code | Code |
| 📖 | doc | Documentation |
| 🎨 | design | Design |
| 📝 | maintenance | Maintenance |
| 💡 | example | Examples |
| 🚧 | test | Tests |
| ⚠️ | bug | Bug reports |
| 答疑 | question | Questions |
| 🤔 | ideas | Ideas, Planning, & Feedback |
| 🔍 | review | Code Review |
| 🌍 | translation | Translation |
| 💰 | financial | Financial contributions |
| 🎉 | fond | Fond memory |

## Checking Status

```bash
npx all-contributors-cli check
```

## Generating Table

```bash
npx all-contributors-cli generate
```

